Original sin is in all of our genetic makeup! Pick a sin, you'll find someone who is so drawn toward it that they &quot;can't help themselves&quot;. It's a pathetic excuse, and attempting to label God as &quot;unfair&quot; for some reason due to it are just as pathetic. Everyone is equally screwed here, sorry. <br>
